structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS

law.text: Nothing in KRS 97.425 to 97.485 shall be construed to conflict with the provisions of KRS 97.020.
law.history: Amended 2007 Ky. Acts ch. 10, sec. 4, effective June 26, 2007. -- Amended 1966 Ky. Acts ch. 255, sec. 115. -- Created 1956 Ky. Acts ch. 25, secs. 9 and 10.
